main event: A civilian in Houston, Texas observed a round object with blinking colored lights on June 3, 1966.
interesting points: The object appeared to be the size of a 21-inch TV screen and had white lights that blinked like a car turn signal.
The object had flashing red, blue, and green lights that twinkled.
The object was observed for 5-10 minutes at a distance of 200-300 yards.
Other similar sightings in the area had been reported.
The witness described the object as a 'brilliant circular light' that moved horizontally at a low altitude.
sighted object: a round object with blinking colored lights
